caption.title: Spatial distribution of urban (red) and rural (blue) H7N9 infections from the first to the fifth epidemic waves (W1 to W5) from April 2013 to June 2017 in the Zhejiang province, China.
caption.p: W1: First wave (April 3—April 27, 2013); W2: Second wave (October 15, 2013—June 16, 2014); W3: Third wave (November 26, 2014—June 2, 2015); W4: Forth wave (September 26, 2015—June 29, 2016); W5: Fifth wave (October 8, 2016—June 12, 2017).
